➜我国自主三代核电“华龙一号”全球首堆首次达到临界状态
http://www.sohu.com/a/426486269_162522	18523
<p><span>来源：<span>中新网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-10-22 13:05</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201022/7981140003f64d85b793529395a17e3a.jpeg" /></i></p>
